cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.HC

This paper is about developing a multi-agent reinforcement learning approach for optimizing multiple recommendation strategies in a sequential manner. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves data analysis and modeling, which could fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, since the proposed approach is evaluated on a real e-commerce platform, it could also be relevant to cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
